---
title: Thai Coconut Pork Meatballs with Sweet Rice & Roasted Green Beans
description: Mad for meatballs but ready to break out of your usual routine? Well you’re in luck, because this ballin’ dish has just the thing. This week, our chefs ditched classic marinara sauce and spaghetti for a coconut-chili-lime sauce and a bed of sweet coconut-scented rice. As a bonus, they’re also throwing in tender roasted green beans and a scattering of scallions and crunchy peanuts. Say hasta la vista to pasta and prepare yourself for a Thai-inspired flavor explosion.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-coconut-meatballs-bb34c192.jpg
